---
title: Sticky Beef Mince & Udon Noodle Stir-Fry  with Asian Greens & Crushed Peanuts
description: A stir-fry sauce can do no wrong, in fact it’s perfection when cooked with beef mince, creating lovely sticky flavours. There are veggies and fragrant garlic rice to absorb all the leftover sauce. It’s too good to miss!

*We’ve replaced the
jasmine rice in this
recipe with udon noodles
due to local ingredient
availability. It’ll be just as
delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65cf01afc7e39206a705aa22-a478d2a5.jpeg
